A truck breakdown or a two destinations with ship from two truck (from intermediate location). One may be a outsidecarrier.
What is common location:
-----------------
common locations are common pickup points(e.g Selkirk,Brookfield,) used by different customers.
To find out the customer codes: use code tabl to enter their location codes.
common locations may be a dropoff point too.
